description: Light Premium task light - enjoy the future of home lighting with this fully dimmable, ultra-bright light - perfect as a wall sconce, cabinet light, handheld utility light and more Motion and touch activated - use the on/auto/off button with a simple touch, choosing between constant illumination or motion activation Effortless installation - mount your task light with the included screws and anchors for permanent placement, attach it to any metallic surface with the built-in magnet backing or set it anywhere using the kickstand Wire-free operation - powered by 6 AA batteries (not included), this product keeps things simple by eliminating any need for complicated wiring - it also saves energy by deactivating after 60-minute in the on setting
